t timidly flees as soon as it finds itself alone."}, {"version": "firered", "text": "It lives in massive rivers that course through jungles. It swarms prey that enter its territory."}, {"version": "heartgold", "text": "They form packs to attack boats and rip out their hulls to sink them. They live in rivers in the jungle."}, {"version": "leafgreen", "text": "It lives in massive rivers that course through jungles. It swarms prey that enter its territory."}, {"version": "moon", "text": "If they scent the faintest trace of blood, they rush to attack en masse. When alone, they\u2019re rather cowardly."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "Carvanha\u2019s strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls. Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this Pok\u00e9mon."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."}, {"version": "ruby", "text": "CARVANHA\u2019s strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls. Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this POK\u00e9MON."}, {"version": "sapphire", "text": "If anything invades CARVANHA\u2019s territory, it will swarm and tear at the intruder with its pointed fangs. On its own, however, this POK\u00e9MON turns suddenly timid."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "These Pok\u00e9mon have sharp fangs and powerful jaws. Sailors avoid Carvanha dens at all costs."}, {"version": "soulsilver", "text": "They form packs to attack boats and rip out their hulls to sink them. They live in rivers in the jungle."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "Each school has its own territory. Any intruders are mercilessly attacked with fangs bared."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "It won\u2019t attack while it\u2019s alone\u2014not even if it spots prey. Instead, it waits for other Carvanha to join it, and then the Pok\u00e9mon attack as a group."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "With its sturdy jaws and fangs, it can easily chomp wooden boats to splinters. It fights with Basculin over food."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "They\u2019re such cowards that they won\u2019t hunt alone. When five or so of them get together, they suddenly turn ferocious!"}, {"version": "white", "text": "They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "They swarm any foe that invades their territory. Their sharp fangs can tear out boat hulls."}, {"version": "x", "text": "They form packs to attack boats and rip out their hulls to sink them. They live in rivers in the jungle."}, {"version": "y", "text": "It lives in massive rivers that course through jungles. It swarms prey that enter its territory."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "diamond", "emerald", "firered", "heartgold", "leafgreen", "moon", "omega-ruby", "pearl", "platinum", "ruby", "sapphire", "shield", "soulsilver", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "brilliant-diamond-shining-pearl", "colosseum", "diamond-pearl", "emerald", "firered-leafgreen", "heartgold-soulsilver", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "platinum", "ruby-sapphire", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y", "xd"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "carvanha"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "sharpedo"}]}